Sorry to hear that your head hurts. There could be many reasons for a headache. Can you tell me more about it? 

* How long have you been experiencing the headache?
* Is it a sharp, dull, or throbbing pain?
* Is the pain located on one side of your head or all over?
* Have you recently been stressed, slept poorly, or eaten something unusual?
* Have you taken any medications or tried any remedies to relieve the pain?

This will help me narrow down some possible causes and offer suggestions to help you feel better.
